Name: alfonslistener
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Package to run a script when a packet is published to a topic on Alfons
Home-page: https://github.com/ntoonio/AlfonsListener
Author: Anton Lindroth
Author-email: ntoonio@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: # Alfons Listener
        Simple program for listening on a topic and when it's received running a script.
        
        ## Setup
        ### config.yaml
        	info:
        	    server: "host:port"
        	    username: "username"
        	    password: "iot"
        	    ssl: True
        
        	commands:
        	  - topic: "topic"
        	    script: "script-to-run"
        	  - topic: "topic2"
        	    python: "module:function"
        	    script: "script-to-run2"
        
        ### Creating a daemon
        
        	$ ./service_install.sh
        
        If you want to install the service under a name other than "alfonslistener" you can change the `name` variable on the top of the file.
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
